Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 会议正式开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎各位出席商店街青年部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:02:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,庙会活动委员临时集会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我是今天的主席
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,羽泽咖啡厅的羽泽鸫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来开始点名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,山吹面包房的沙绫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,北泽肉铺的育美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.74,0:03:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好次～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,青年部太鼓带头人巴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,和她的妹妹亚子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,再为吾呈上暗黑的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,甘甜又气泡充足的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一杯可乐是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,话说你怎么在这儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,有商店街之处必有我摩卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,她是山吹面包房的常客了
Comment: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,OPCN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我们还迎来了一位新成员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,旭汤的朝日六花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我作为Galaxy的工作人员跟各位见面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,请大家多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我是受店长委托
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可是还不是很清楚状况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们几个也在慢慢摸索着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,其实吧 是这次商店街要搞个活动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我看到海报了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,「身心健康 Go Go」庙会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,健康Go！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,之前我被商店街的老一辈们点了名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想招呼一批年轻人进来保持商店街的活力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,小鸫 来弄一个Love啥的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就那个Love
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Love？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是和巴一起弄了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,乐器的演奏会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你说演唱会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}Live
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真怀念咱的青春时代啊 小米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,咱几个也穿校服整了一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,三味线的演奏会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,高中生最棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好青春呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,然后Afterglow就决定要出演了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,听说商店街的各个店铺都会帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:04:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello-Happy你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要弄可乐饼Live哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可乐饼Live？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,PoPiPa的各位不出场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 想法不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起来肯定更开心的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能去问一声呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 虽然已经能猜到回答了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,去！当然想去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们主办的演唱会那边没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,现在正在列场地的清单呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是我做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那个庙会是每年都办的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我们家会摆摊卖面包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,还有育美家的可乐饼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那个可好吃了 含税才86日元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那会场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说会在户外现搭一个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,露天演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊 露天演唱会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,说了两遍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟很重要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,露天演唱会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,第三遍！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,相当重要哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就回复她们说要参加哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要和Afterglow一起演出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:05:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,还得决定曲目呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,得开始练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起来拼命练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,巴 节奏太赶了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我太期待健康Go啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,巴你最喜欢庙会了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,太鼓那边要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还用说吗 当然也全力以赴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,加油哦 小巴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,再不快点山吹面包房就要关门了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然要面对吃不上面包的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我找不到活下去的意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那就快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好次～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,听说是在这里搭建舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,商店街的老一辈现在也很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 她们好像还做了团扇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,燃起来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,预备 一 二 哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为巴你也会配合的 好过分！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这部分就照往常来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,绯玛丽好来劲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,休息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,给各位奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是巧克力螺好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟这是山吹面包房的所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,干脆把店名加进歌词里弄成广告一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,想买面包哪里去？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就去山吹面包房～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不买呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,难得一场庙会 还是想尽兴一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要唱Happy Happy Party？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定嗨得起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,曲目编排就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 还不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.33,0:08:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Galaxy已经同意给我们租器材了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们提前一天去搬出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好来劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因为又要准备庙会 又想多练习一些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要是太努力又累倒了可不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是哦 那我会尽量不累倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,又来劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,还是一如既往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你们啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,夕阳好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在初中的学园祭表演之后看到的夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么可能忘记呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那毕竟是我们的第一场演出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之后也看了好多次夕阳呢 我们五个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 这不是LOCK吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,LOCK！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\an7\1a&H30&\1cF5CAFF\blur2\bord0\pos(30,-80)}m 10 120 l 10 270 780 270 780 120
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\fnDQKLDGSU}竟然！意想不到！Poppin'Party也决定参演！！\N{\b0\fs35}这是一支由（各位成员）组成的\N既可爱又让人心动的乐队，真的非常可爱！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Poppin'Party也决定参演
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,快给我拿下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,特意为我们贴的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 LOCK！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是咱们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.39,0:09:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那是之前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Poppin'Party 即将开演！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是LOCK特意帮我们做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,还想在这边唱歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是最后一件了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那就搬去舞台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 蔬菜店会用车帮我们运过去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.01,0:10:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,弄完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,真期待明天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,大家要玩得尽兴哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家风雨兼程
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我宣布 第19届身心健康 Go Go庙会 正式开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,请看可乐饼Live
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我买二十个！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,因为庙会名字有Go
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:56.52,Tips,,0,0,0,,注：日语“五”与英文Go发音相近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,所以五百日元Go Go！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Go Go！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:11:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是Afterglow
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,第一首曲子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然下起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,下雨吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不好 那些设备！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,只能再把它们搬回Galaxy了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我去帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我去叫好卡车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,原定在庙会广场进行的演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.74,0:11:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,因下雨暂时中止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,再重复一遍…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不介意的话就用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 是羽泽咖啡厅的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这雨会停吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,天气预报虽然说到了傍晚就会停
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,鞋子都湿透了 兴致全被浇没了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我好想演出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是亚子送的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我也有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,大家也把它分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 山吹面包房
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我开吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.55,0:12:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,巧克力螺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你们已经习惯露天演唱会了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.39,0:12:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我看你们都那么冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.23,0:12:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,现在也只能等着啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不管发生什么 都只是照常发挥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Afterglow是怎么聚在一起的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就是回过神来就在一起了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟都是一起长大的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,小学还在同一个班呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是初二的时候 只有兰被分到了别的班
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,然后五个人就难得见一面了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,乐队…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,来组乐队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 鸫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:13:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我想过怎么让我们五个人又能在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,所以觉得大家一起办一件事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一定会有很多时间聚起来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我觉得可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好像好久没看到兰的这种表情了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,想到什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Omnis 意思是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然听着很帅 但总感觉不对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultra Violet
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,紫外线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,还是取个有意义的名字比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟乐队叫紫外线的 还是太难懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要有我们风格的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,夕阳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们总是在放学之后练习
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不就是傍晚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,翻译成英语的话
Comment: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,(Sunset,日落)？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunset？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}日落
Comment: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,(Evening,夜晚)？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Evening？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Afterglow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这个名字觉得如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,决定了 我们的乐队名字就叫Afterglow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你们一直都在一起的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,简单说来就是难舍难分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟都经历过那么多事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,有的有的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 咱还有个大目标对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,朝着武道馆前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,武道馆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还是像平常一样在一起才最开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,感受到了各位深厚的友情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,太夸张啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,雨小了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎停了 能不能再开演呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,现在开始准备的话 应该能赶得上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但是舞台就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,还有拖把吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 放在商店街的仓库里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们去搬器材吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不能再用车了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,诶～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不行的啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好重
